val nameOrPrefix = ""
val transformedDF = sqlContext
  .read
  .format("csv")
  .option("inferSchema", "true")
  .load(s"file:///tmp/${nameOrPrefix}/transformed-df.csv")
  .toDF("imagePath", "pcaVector", "pixelVector", "scaledPixelVector")

z.show(transformedDF.limit(10))

//////////////////////////////////////////////
// May Need to Update Given Image Path      //
//////////////////////////////////////////////

import org.apache.spark.sql.Row
import com.advancedspark.ml.Similarity 
import org.apache.spark.mllib.linalg.DenseVector
import org.jblas.DoubleMatrix

// Given Image Path: Tom_Cruise_0006.jpg
val givenItemId = "/root/pipeline/datasets/eigenface/lfw-deepfunneled/Tom_Cruise/Tom_Cruise_0001.jpg"
val givenItemFactors = transformedDF.select($"imagePath", $"pcaVector")
  .where($"imagePath" === givenItemId)
  .map(row => row.get(1).asInstanceOf[DenseVector].toArray)
  .collect()(0)

// Convert Array[Double] to DoubleMatrix
val givenItemFactorsMatrix = new DoubleMatrix(givenItemFactors)

// Find Other Similar Items to the Given Item
val similarItems = transformedDF.select($"imagePath", $"pcaVector")
  .filter($"imagePath" !== givenItemId)
  .map{ row =>
     val itemId = row.getString(0)
     val otherItemFactors = row.get(1).asInstanceOf[DenseVector].toArray
     val otherItemFactorsMatrix = new DoubleMatrix(otherItemFactors)
     val similarity = 
       Similarity.cosineSimilarity(otherItemFactorsMatrix, givenItemFactorsMatrix)
     (itemId, similarity)
  }
  
// Sort and Return Top 5 Items by Similarity to Given Item
val sortedSimilarItems = similarItems.top(5)(Ordering.by[(String, Double), Double] { case (id, similarity) => similarity })

val sortedSimilarItemsDF = 
  sqlContext.createDataFrame(sortedSimilarItems).toDF("similarItemId", "similarity")

z.show(sortedSimilarItemsDF.select($"similarItemId", $"similarity"))
